div.p:
Penalties not yet reported are as follows: Sofia court trying those accused of
                    persecution of Jews, to death 2 (in absentia) and 3 others (also in absentia) to
                    life, 21 others to lesser terms of imprisonment; Turgovishte, to death 25, to
                    imprisonment 62; Karlovo, to death none, to imprisonment 35; Vratza, to death
                    none, to imprisonment 28; Starazagora, to death 28, to imprisonment 77;
                    Kustendil, to death 33, imprisonment 95; Sevlievo, to death 41, imprisonment 77;
                    Rustchuk, to death 6, imprisonment 22; Silistra, to death 7, imprisonment 2;
                    Isperich, to death none, imprisonment 24.
